'''西洋接骨木'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Sambucus nigra''}}）为[[五福花科|五福花科]][[接骨木属|接骨木属]]的植物。原產於歐洲和北美洲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Sambucus&SPECIES_XREF=nigra&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|title=Flora Europaea Search Results|website=Rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk|accessdate=2017-10-13|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206061429/http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Sambucus&SPECIES_XREF=nigra&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Sambucus&SPECIES_XREF=nigra&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|title=Flora Europaea Search Results|website=Rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk|accessdate=13 October 2017|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206061429/http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Sambucus&SPECIES_XREF=nigra&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來人工引種到世界其他地區。

其[[种加词|种加词]]“''nigra''”意为“黑色的，暗色的”。

== 形态 ==
落叶[[乔木|乔木]]或[[灌木|大灌木]]，达4-10米，幼枝具纵条纹，空心<ref>Vedel, H. and Lange, J. 1971. ''Trees and Bushes in Wood and Hedgerow''. p.196. Methuen and Co. Ltd. {{ISBN|0416-61780-8}}</ref>
。二年生枝黄褐色，具明显突起的圆形皮孔；髓部发达，白色。
===叶===
羽状复叶有小叶1-3对，通常2对，具短柄，椭圆形或椭圆状卵形，长4-10cm，宽2-3.5cm，顶端尖或尾尖，边缘具锐锯齿，基部楔形或阔楔形至钝圆而两侧不等，揉碎后有恶臭，中脉基部、小叶柄基部及叶轴均被短柔毛；托叶叶状或退化成腺形。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://frps.eflora.cn/frps/Sambucus%20nigra | title = 西洋接骨木 | work = 《中国植物志》第72卷 | publisher = 科学出版社 | author = 中国科学院 | date = 1988 | accessdate = 2012-10-18 | archive-date = 2018-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180311140736/http://frps.eflora.cn/frps/Sambucus%20nigra | dead-url = no }}</ref>
